item.title: WebClient Running Help!
item.dc:creator: @RiiPiiNFtW RiiPiiNFtW
item.description:
@RiiPiiNFtW wrote:

My guess is the client was compiled with JDK7 and now it is being attempted to be ran through a lower JDK package.

FYI: Classes compiled by JDK6 and read by JDK7 are completely fine. However, Classes compiled by JDK7 trying to be read by JDK6 will not work.

Try not to double post. Someone will eventually get to you.

Read full topic
